HEADWORD: Guanin
<hw>Gua"nin</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Physiol. Chem.)</fld>
<def>A crystalline substance (<chform>C5H5N5O</chform>) contained in
guano. It is also a constituent of the liver, pancreas, and other glands
in mammals.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Guano</ent>⟦br⟧
